INSTALLATION GUIDELINE
----------------------

1. Untar the .zip file
	

2. Make sure that CRF++0.51 is install in your system 

3. Make sure 5.10.0 and above is installed in the system



EXECUTE
-------
To train the tagger

	btrain.bat <train_data_file> 


To test the tagger
	
	use btest.bat <file name> 

		the input file can be in UTF-8 encoded or ASCII encoded text
		system gives the output in 'pos_op' 		 

